<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="97" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="97">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="97">
Four isolates clustered in a clade distinct from its closest phylogenetic neighbour, 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tectonae" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tectonae">D. tectonae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tulliensis" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tulliensis">D. tulliensis</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" family="Diaporthaceae" genus="Diaporthe" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Diaporthe alangii" order="Diaporthales" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="alangii">Diaporthe alangii</taxonomicName>
can be distinguished from 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tectonae" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tectonae">D. tectonae</taxonomicName>
in cal, tef1 and tub2 loci (6/458 in cal, 4/308 in tef1 and 11/407 in tub2); from 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tulliensis" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tulliensis">D. tulliensis</taxonomicName>
in ITS, tef1 and tub2 loci (6/462 in ITS, 8/308 in tef1 and 10/701 in tub2). Morphologically, 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. alangii" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="alangii">D. alangii</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tectonae" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tectonae">D. tectonae</taxonomicName>
in shorter conidiophores (6-12 vs. 11-18 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
) and longer alpha conidia (6.5-8 vs. 5.5-6 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
); from 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. tulliensis" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="tulliensis">D. tulliensis</taxonomicName>
in shorter conidiophores (6-12 vs. 15-20 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Crous, PW" journalOrPublisher="Persoonia: Molecular Phylogeny and Evolution of Fungi" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" url="https://doi.org/10.3767/003158515X690269" year="2015">Crous et al. 2015</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Doilom, M" journalOrPublisher="Fungal Diversity" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" pagination="107 - 182" title="Microfungi on Tectonagrandis (teak) in Northern Thailand." url="https://doi.org/10.1007/s13225-016-0368-7" volume="82" year="2017">Doilom et al. 2017</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
